  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430160/extras/bc6a4ad2420999d751b5fe93390b9964.poster.avif?t=1755292538\" width=100 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430160/extras/bc6a4ad2420999d751b5fe93390b9964.webm?t=1755292538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430160/extras/bc6a4ad2420999d751b5fe93390b9964.mp4?t=1755292538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This is a <i><strong>Fungi.</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be playing as a group of them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fungi can cling to almost anything. as well as to each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >as the Fungi you will to traverse terrain, solve puzzles, and find new and interesting ways to cling to each other to best the many challenges of the wastelands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430160/extras/9899ca04ec6a4c0b0f786fd24fd7f8f8.avif?t=1755292538\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430160/extras_big/9899ca04ec6a4c0b0f786fd24fd7f8f8.webp?t=1755292538 width=1560 height=1035 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique hand drawn graphics </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special made music for almost every level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seamlessly integrated narrative through level design, cutscenes, and diary entries </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique and intriguing movement mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creative physics based logic puzzles using the special movement of the Fungi</p></li></ul>",
